<div class="job-details-section pt-120" id="job-details">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center gy-5">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="job-details-wrap">
                    <h3>UX Researcher Job Description</h3>
                    <p class="para mb-4">A UX Researcher is a professional who systematically studies target users to collect and analyze data that will help inform the product design process.</p>
                    <h4>Job brief :</h4>
                    <p class="para">We are looking for a UX Researcher to join our team and implement various UX designs into our programs and computer systems based on the need of users to ensure customers have an enjoyable experience when using our products. </p>
                    <p class="para mb-4">UX Researcher responsibilities include conducting user research and working with the design team to implement design choices to improve user experience.</p>
                    <h4>Responsibilities :</h4>
                    <ul class="about-list">
                        <li>Price of additional materials or parts (if needed)</li>
                        <li>Transportation cost for carrying new materials/parts</li>
                        <li>Interpreting services is our specialty</li>
                    </ul>
                    <h4>Software Skill’s :</h4>
                    <p class="para">Adobe Photoshop, Illustrator, Figma, Adobe XD, Sketch etc </p>
                    <h4>Salary :</h4>
                    <p class="para">25K to 100k </p>
                    <h4>Job Type :</h4>
                    <p class="para">Remote/ Office</p>
                    <h4>Location :</h4>
                    <p class="para">House#01, Road#05, XYZ</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="apply-form">
                    <div class="apply-form-title">
                        <h4>Apply for a Position:</h4>
                        <p>Please complete the form below to apply for a position :</p>
                    </div>
                    <form>
                        <div class="row g-4">
                            <div class="col-lg-6">
                                <div class="form-inner">
                                    <input type="text" name="fname" placeholder="Your Name:">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-6">
                                <div class="form-inner">
                                    <input type="text" name="fname" placeholder="Phone Number:">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-12">
                                <div class="form-inner">
                                    <input type="text" name="fname" placeholder="Typing for Position :">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-12">
                                <div class="form-inner">
                                    <input type="text" name="fname" placeholder="Experience:">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-12">
                                <div class="form-inner">
<textarea name="message" cols="30" rows="6" placeholder="Cover Letter :"></textarea>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-12">
                                <div class="form-inner">
                                    <label for="cv" class="mb-3">Upload Resume :</label>
                                    <input type="file">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                                <input type="submit" value="Send Now" class="eg-btn btn--submit">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
